  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Light Tab</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_icon.png?5179c5\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/32px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/32px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n<dl><dd><span class=\"dablink\"><i>For the filter in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a>, see <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Light_Sources_Filter\" title=\"Light Sources Filter\">Light Sources Filter</a>.</i></span></dd></dl>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Icon_Light.png\" class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Icon_Light.png?6f6120\" width=\"105\" height=\"128\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Icon_Light.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Tab Icon</div></div></div>\n<div><b>“</b><span>Sure beats darkness.</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wilson\" title=\"Wilson\">Wilson</a></p>\n</div>\n<p>Light is used to illuminate the world at <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Night\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Night\">Night</a>, lowering the rate at which <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sanity\" title=\"Sanity\">Sanity</a> decreases and protecting against <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Charlie\" title=\"Charlie\">Charlie</a>, who will attack in total darkness.\n</p><p><span class=\"box headnote\"><i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Glommer%27s_Flower.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Glommer&#x27;s Flower.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Glommer%27s_Flower.png/25px-Glommer%27s_Flower.png?22167d\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\"></a> See also: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Charlie#Light_Sources\" title=\"Charlie\">Light Sources</a> </i></span><br>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Downloadable_Content\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Gift_Icon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Gift Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Gift_Icon.png/32px-Gift_Icon.png?8b4efa\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Downloadable Content</span></h2>\n<p>In the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Reign of Giants\">Reign of Giants</a></i> DLC, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Endothermic_Fire\" title=\"Endothermic Fire\">Endothermic Fires</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Endothermic_Fire_Pit\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Endothermic Fire Pit\">Endothermic Fire Pits</a>, and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moggles\" title=\"Moggles\">Moggles</a> were added to the Light Tab.\n</p><p>In the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shipwrecked\">Shipwrecked</a></i> DLC, the player can craft <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Chiminea\" title=\"Chiminea\">Chimineas</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Buoyant_Chiminea\" title=\"Buoyant Chiminea\">Buoyant Chimineas</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tar_Lamp\" title=\"Tar Lamp\">Tar Lamps</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Obsidian_Fire_Pit\" title=\"Obsidian Fire Pit\">Obsidian Fire Pits</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bottle_Lantern\" title=\"Bottle Lantern\">Bottle Lanterns</a> in the Light Tab. This DLC also includes Endothermic Fires and Endothermic Fire Pits. Additionally, the two light sources that can be attached to <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Boats\" title=\"Boats\">Boats</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Boat_Torch\" title=\"Boat Torch\">Boat Torches</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Boat_Lantern\" title=\"Boat Lantern\">Boat Lanterns</a>, are available in this tab.\n</p><p>In the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cork_Candle_Hat\" title=\"Cork Candle Hat\">Cork Candle Hats</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cowl\" title=\"Cowl\">Cowls</a> were added to this tab, while Pumpkin Lanterns are not available. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Craftable_Items_and_Structures\">Craftable Items and Structures</span></h2>\n<p>The following items and structures can be crafted in the Light Tab:\n</p>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Campfire\" title=\"Campfire\"><img alt=\"Campfire\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Campfire.png?fc5405\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Campfire\" title=\"Campfire\">Campfire</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fire_Pit\" title=\"Fire Pit\"><img alt=\"Fire Pit\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fire_Pit.png?d519eb\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fire_Pit\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fire Pit\">Fire Pit</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Torch\" title=\"Torch\"><img alt=\"Torch\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Torch.png?9f75f2\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Torch\" title=\"Torch\">Torch</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Miner_Hat\" title=\"Miner Hat\"><img alt=\"Miner Hat\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Miner_Hat.png?d01e11\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Miner_Hat\" title=\"Miner Hat\">Miner Hat</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pumpkin_Lantern\" title=\"Pumpkin Lantern\"><img alt=\"Pumpkin Lantern\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pumpkin_Lantern.png?bb341e\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pumpkin_Lantern\" title=\"Pumpkin Lantern\">Pumpkin Lantern</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lantern\" title=\"Lantern\"><img alt=\"Lantern\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lantern.png?dc0f6a\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lantern\" title=\"Lantern\">Lantern</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"ga