  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Ánh sáng được sử dụng để chiếu sáng thế giới vào Ban đêm, làm giảm tốc độ suy giảm Tinh thần và bảo vệ khỏi Charlie, kẻ sẽ tấn công trong bóng tối hoàn toàn.</p>",
  "title": "Light Tab",
  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Don't Starve|Reign of Giants|Shipwrecked|Hamlet}}\n{{for|the filter in [[Don't Starve Together]]|Light Sources Filter}}\n[[File:Icon Light.png|thumb|Tab Icon]]\n{{Quote|Sure beats darkness.|Wilson}}\nLight is used to illuminate the world at [[Night]], lowering the rate at which [[Sanity]] decreases and protecting against [[Charlie]], who will attack in total darkness.\n\n{{See also|Charlie#Light_Sources|l1=Light Sources}}\n==[[File:Gift Icon.png|32px]] Downloadable Content==\nIn the ''[[Reign of Giants]]'' DLC, [[Endothermic Fire]]s, [[Endothermic Fire Pit]]s, and [[Moggles]] were added to the Light Tab.\n\nIn the ''[[Shipwrecked]]'' DLC, the player can craft [[Chiminea]]s, [[Buoyant Chiminea]]s, [[Tar Lamp]]s, [[Obsidian Fire Pit]]s and [[Bottle Lantern]]s in the Light Tab. This DLC also includes Endothermic Fires and Endothermic Fire Pits. Additionally, the two light sources that can be attached to [[Boats]], [[Boat Torch]]es and [[Boat Lantern]]s, are available in this tab.\n\nIn the ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC, [[Cork Candle Hat]]s and [[Cowl]]s were added to this tab, while Pumpkin Lanterns are not available. \n\n==Craftable Items and Structures==\nThe following items and structures can be crafted in the Light Tab:\n\n<gallery columns=\"6\" position=\"center\" widths=\"70\" captionalign=\"center\" captionsize=\"medium\" bordersize=\"none\" spacing=\"medium\" hideaddbutton=\"true\" navigation=\"true\">\nCampfire.png|[[Campfire]]|link=Campfire\nFire Pit.png|[[Fire Pit]]|link=Fire Pit\nTorch.png|[[Torch]]|link=Torch\nMiner Hat.png|[[Miner Hat]]|link=Miner Hat\nPumpkin Lantern.png|[[Pumpkin Lantern]]|link=Pumpkin Lantern\nLantern.png|[[Lantern]]|link=Lantern\nEndothermic Fire.png|[[Endothermic Fire]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Endothermic Fire\nEndothermic Fire Pit.png|[[Endothermic Fire Pit]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Endothermic Fire\nMoggles.png|[[Moggles]]<br>{{Pic|20|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}|link=Moggles\nChiminea.png|[[Chiminea]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Chiminea\nBuoyant Chiminea.png|[[Buoyant Chiminea]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Buoyant Chiminea\nTar Lamp.png|[[Tar Lamp]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Tar Lamp\nObsidian Fire Pit.png|[[Obsidian Fire Pit]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Obsidian Fire Pit\nBottle Lantern.png|[[Bottle Lantern]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Bottle Lantern\nBoat Torch.png|[[Boat Torch]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Boat Torch\nBoat Lantern.png|[[Boat Lantern]]<br>{{Pic|20|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}|link=Boat Lantern\nCork Candle Hat.png|[[Cork Candle Hat]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}|link=Cork Candle Hat\nCowl.png|[[Cowl]]<br>{{Pic|20|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}}|link=Cowl\n</gallery>\n\n{{Tabs}}\n__NOTOC__\n[[it:Fonti di Luce]]\n[[ru:Освещение]]\n[[pl:Światło]]\n[[ko:광원 탭]]"
}
